OL,3,CRHS Harlow Carr unveil emergency
OL,4,Cdrought plans
OL,6,FThe Royal Horticultural Society (RHS)
OL,7,Fhas unveiled emergency plans to
OL,8,Fprotect its gardens from the potential
OL,9,Ffor major water shortages in the
OL,10,Ffuture.
OL,12,FThe environmental charity, which owns
OL,13,Fand operates RHS Harlow Carr near
OL,14,FHarrogate alongside four other
OL,15,Frenowned public gardens in England,
OL,16,Fsaid on Saturday 24 January it will
OL,17,Finvest in more water capture and
OL,18,Fmanagement projects than anything else
OL,19,Fin 2026 following severe droughts last
OL,20,Fyear.
