OL,3,CRHS Harlow Carr unveil emergency
OL,4,Cdrought plans
OL,6,FIn response to the increasingly
OL,7,Ferratic weather patterns, the RHS is
OL,8,Falso urging gardeners to mirror the
OL,9,Fmeasures it will take this winter and
OL,10,Fspring to prepare for as much rain as
OL,11,Fpossible.
OL,13,FThis includes preparing the soil with
OL,14,Fhollow tining, chop-and-drop and
OL,15,Fmulching, creating rain gardens,
OL,16,Finstalling rainwater storage
OL,17,Ffacilities, and thinking about whether
OL,18,Fplants are in the right place.
