OL,3,CRHS Harlow Carr unveil emergency
OL,4,Cdrought plans
OL,6,FIt comes as global warming continues
OL,7,Fto drive volatility in the global
OL,8,Fwater cycle, with the UK seeing more
OL,9,Ffrequent years of below average
OL,10,Frainfall and a growing risk of
OL,11,Fflooding.
OL,13,FLast year Yorkshire saw the driest
OL,14,Fspring in 132 years and the hottest
OL,15,Fsummer since records began, plunging
OL,16,Fseveral areas into drought, with
OL,17,FYorkshire water bringing in a hosepipe
OL,18,Fban which was only lifted in December.
