OL,3,CRHS Harlow Carr unveil emergency
OL,4,Cdrought plans
OL,6,FIn preparation the RHS are looking at
OL,7,Fhow they can distribute water supplies
OL,8,Fbetween it's sites.
OL,10,FProjects in 2026 will include
OL,11,Fincreasing the storage of water in
OL,12,Ftanks and lakes, to make the most of
OL,13,Fwinter rainfall.
OL,15,FFiona Slight a curator at RHS Harlow
OL,16,FCarr said, "At this time of year the
OL,17,Fstream is in full flow, we feel like
OL,18,Fwe have no problem.
