OL,6,F"Come the summer, when we don't have
OL,7,Fthe rainfall and there is nothing
OL,8,Fcoming into the beck, that's when you
OL,9,Fhave to think in the winter, how do we
OL,10,Fcapture water the water that you have."
OL,12,FThey are also installing ebb and flow
OL,13,Fbenches in its retail centres to
OL,14,Freduce water use, and investing in
OL,15,Frain garden installations.
OL,17,FThe charity will also carry out
OL,18,Fresearch on soil health in its gardens
OL,19,Fas well as continue quantifying
OL,20,Findividual plant and whole landscape
OL,21,Fwater use.
