OL,6,FIn addition, it will explore using
OL,7,Fmore grey-water ` cleaner wastewater
OL,8,Ffrom baths, showers, sinks and washing
OL,9,Fmachines.
OL,11,FThe plans mark a wider shift in the
OL,12,Forganisation's approach to climate
OL,13,Fchange as it increasingly focuses on
OL,14,Fadapting to the growing impacts over
OL,15,Fmitigating the rise in planet-warming
OL,16,Femissions in the atmosphere.
