OL,3,CRHS Harlow Carr unveil emergency
OL,4,Cdrought plans
OL,6,FTim Upson, RHS director of
OL,7,Fhorticulture, said, "Water is the
OL,8,Flifeblood of any garden ` important
OL,9,Fnot only to human health and wellbeing
OL,10,Fbut the broader environment and
OL,11,Fwildlife ` and we, like the UK's 34
OL,12,Fmillion gardeners, are having to adapt
OL,13,Fto the new normal; prioritising
OL,14,Fcollection, storage and management of
OL,15,Frainwater as well as relocating and
OL,16,Freassessing our collections to future-
OL,17,Fproof them."
